{{Punjabi/Navigation panel|Conversation}}
You have already learnt the Gurmukhi script for writing Punjabi, the Muharni for speaking Punjabi and some Punjabi vocabulary. In this Module you will learn to use Punjabi for communicating with people.
'''''If you have not mastered the Gurmukhi script and Muharni you are strongly advised to go back to the [[Punjabi/Gurmukhi|Gurmukhi]] script and [[Punjabi/Muharni|Muharni]] modules and practise there thoughly before returning. In this module you will be expected to have basic skill of reading and writing the Punjabi words.'''''
This module contains eight lessons each containing a number of parts and sub parts. Each part along with its sub parts will be learnt in one session of approximately one hour.
{{BookCat}}

