Shouldn't Prepositional case be Instrumental case?

:These are 2 different cases. Пишу ручкой (Instrumental) - "(I) write with a pen". Пишу о ручке (Prepositional) - "(I) write about a pen".--[[User:Atitarev|Atitarev]] ([[User talk:Atitarev|talk]]) 10:36, 23 November 2008 (UTC)

